{
  "stem": "18581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 232.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also used to-- I belonged to a group, also, and the attorney [NON-ENGLISH], and [NON-ENGLISH], and [NON-ENGLISH], we were-- and the-- our teacher, [NON-ENGLISH]-- we were interested in the study of political developments.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a private group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to get also foreign newspapers, including Berliner Tageblatt, and [NON-ENGLISH], and-- and-- and others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we knew exactly what everybody else knew about Nazism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody knew at that time the final solution aims of Hitler, which were formulated, I believe, in [NON-ENGLISH] in 1942, after Hitler noticed from the Evian conference that no country, including the United States, wants the Jews.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he decided that Jews are sort of fair game.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Especially when the ship St.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Louis returned-- was-- went around the world, came back to-- so we knew all about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew already in '39, and of course, it was-- I don't know when the ship was-- was going.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we knew all that was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew about camps in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because while there was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a control of the press and so on, but some news were always printed about camps in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you must realize that Lithuania and Germany were not on the best terms, because of the dispute over Memel, over Klaipeda.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So sometimes they used to print in the Yiddish papers, but also the Lithuanian papers, about the atrocities, and about the-- so on and [INAUDIBLE] the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And others.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew all about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew of Stalin that he was a dictator of-- of Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And most of what we knew was negative.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
